body.description: Bella the Dream Seeker is your magical friend who wants to share her dreams and inspire you to follow yours. This magical looking fairy with her sweet outfit and posable long arms and legs will become your best friend because she has similar hopes and dreams. Bella sits in her Dreamy Moon Packaging which has special place for you to write your very own Dreams. Your Dream Seeker will keep your dream safe and wish for it to come true. Bella is an animal lover! She dreams that all animals will be treated with love and kindness! Her magical outfit reflects this in her edgy kitty inspired style with her purrrfect accessories! Her layered Pom-pom skirt is removeable along with her cute molded sneakers! Her bright pink deluxe glitter tulle wings give her such a cool style! With delicately rooted gorgeous long hair individually designed hair ribbons, she loves being brushed and styled. Bella's face is highly detailed and full of expression with huge adorable eyes! On every Dream Seeker's wrist you will find their beautiful and unique ""Dream Mark"". Their ""Dream Mark"" represents the Doll's personality and the dream that they seek! Bella has the ""Dream Mark"" of Kindness. Bella's fabric body and long arms and legs can be easily posed so that you can display your magical Dream Seeker on their own Dreamy Moon Packaging. There are two other charming Dream Seeker Dolls to discover - Hope and Luna! Create an enchanting display in your room! Follow your Dreams today with a special friend!

manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: Dream Seekers are a range of beautifully crafted posable fashion dolls to inspire you to follow your dreams! With unique personalities and style, these girls have no fear in expressing themselves through their fashions and appearance. These inspiring friends share their dreams to encourage and give inspiration to young girls and let them know that the dreams they write inside their Dream Star are possible to reach!

Follow Your Dreams With Bella! Bella the magical Dream Seeker is here to help make your dreams come true! Beautiful and magical, Bella is here to share her dreams and inspire you to follow yours. Bella is an adorable "Ragdoll" inspired fairy with a soft material body and posable long arms and legs who will become your best friend because she has similar hopes and dreams. Dreamy Fashion And Style! Bella is a magical fashion conscious fairy with a magical outfit that reflects her love for animals! She has an edgy kitty inspired style including some purrrfect accessories! Her layered Pom-pom skirt is changeable along with her removeable molded sneakers! Her bright pink deluxe glitter tulle wings give her such a sweet whimsical look! Tell Bella Your Dream. Bella the Dream Seeker sits in her Dreamy Moon Packaging. Inside the Moon Seat is a special place for you to write your dream. Bella will keep your dreams safe and wish for it to come true. She is very good at keeping secrets and helping you reach your dreams!

Beautiful Hair and Fabulous Faces! Each Dream Seeker has delicately rooted gorgeous long hair, perfect for brushing and styling. They also have unique individually designed Dream Ribbons in their hair that match their outfits and personality. Every Dream Seeker Doll has a beautiful, highly detailed and expressive face, with huge adorable printed eyes, detailed lips and delicate complexion! Discover Your Dream Seeker's Dream Mark. Every Dream Seeker Doll has a unique "Dream Mark" on their wrist that represents the Dream they Seek and their personality. Bella has the "Dream Mark" of Kindness and represents the kindness she shows to all animals!. Perhaps her Dream Mark will inspire your dreams! So Sweet And Posable! Dream Seeker Dolls are inspired by beautiful rag dolls styling. With fabric bodies and long arms and legs, they can easily be posed so they sit on their Dreamy Moon Packaging. They make the most beautiful display as they sit and keep your dreams safe!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on June 27, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Cute, but slightly inaccurate to photos
reviews.reviewText: I was intrigued by these because they have completely plush bodies, and the reviews I've seen on YouTube were very positive. I think this doll is so much cuter in person, and her soft body is great for cuddling and displaying! I love the details and the color palette of each of the characters, but I was drawn to Luna most as I used to do ballet! My only complaint about this doll is that it's a little different than the photos; I would have preferred the dream catcher bracelet in the pictures, but for some reason, mine has a little ballet slipper bracelet. The hair also isn't as plentiful as the photos, but neither bits bother me too much as the hair is very soft and the bracelet is still cute; the doll also came with cute hair clips. These dolls are very high-quality and BIG for their price; I highly recommend these for kids and collectors!
